Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.98,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\b0\fs40\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(880,810)}8월 출연 밴드 후보\N\N·마카로니펜슬\N\N·설국 with 터널
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 왜...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,오리지널 곡까지\N만들었는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 이쪽 일이랑\N상관 없고
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..어쩐지\N분위기가...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}곱창났는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,집객 실패했을 때의\N목표치라면 낼 수 있어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,돈 문제가 아니라
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,실력의 문제
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,요전에는\N내보내줬잖아...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 추억만들기용으로\N특별히 해준 거지?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,추억 만들기라니...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,평소에는 데모 음원\N심사 같은 것까지 하고 있다고
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,알면서 그래?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,그..렇긴 한데...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,미안하지만
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,5월 라이브 때같은\N퀄리티라면 못 내보니까
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,못 내보낸다니...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 그럼 우리는...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,평생 너희끼리서\N칭구칭구 클럽이나 하셔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 할 말 더 있냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,그 나이 먹고\N인형 안고 있지 않으면!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,잠도 못 자는 주제에에~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,이지치 선배!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,저 퇴장 대사는\N또 뭐래냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,인형이라면...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,이 너덜너덜한\N판다랑 토끼 말하는 거?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,어머, 깜찍해라~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,그 사진 지워라!\N지금 당장!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 하시는 거예요!?\N쫓아가야죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,에에에...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,귀찮은 티 내지 말구요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른, 고토 씨도!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,가자...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐만, 봇치쨩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,네에...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뭔데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뭔데, 뭐데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뭐임, 뭐임, 뭐임...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(755,980)}딱 보이게\N삐져 있네
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,시꺼...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,저기, 선배...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮으세요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,미안해...\N갑자기 뛰쳐나가서
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 말을\N그렇게 할 것까진 없잖아~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저..저기이...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.73,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(832,470)}떠흑…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.73,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(498.667,552.667)}허억…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,아까...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,허억...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,끅...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,허억, 점챵님히...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩!\N우선 숨부터 쉬자!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,감사합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,좀 진정됐어?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,점장님이\N아까 그러시더라구요...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.33,Above - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\b0\fs40\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(1320,350)}8월 출연 밴드 후보\N\N·마카로니펜실\N\N·설국 with 터널\N\N·ahoge\N\N·이노우에 brothers\N\N·dropout & Reborn\N\N·녹황색야채
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카한테\N좀 전해주라
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브에 나가고 싶으면\N우선은 오디션부터
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,1주일 뒤, 토요일에\N연주 보고 정할 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}..라고
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 하니...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,최..최대한 복종심을\N표현하고자...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른 안 쫒아가면\N애들 놓치지 않겠냐...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 멍!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.67,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(1135,310)}흠흠♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,개가 배를 보여주는\N포즈...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,복종이라기보다는
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,전투하려는 사인을\N나타내는 거라는 설도...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,있다더라?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.29,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(775,620)}흐앙~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,료 선배, 박식하셔~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,근데...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,그게 문제가 아니라...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,다시 말해서...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,오디션!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,거기에 합격하면\N라이브에 나갈 수 있단 거구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 처음부터\N그렇게 말을 하면 되잖아~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,언니는\N심술대장이라니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도, 그럼 남은 건\N열심히 하는 것뿐이네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,응...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응, 응...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,다행이다~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.98,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1755,810)}응, 응!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 그러게...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"얘네 둘이 제일 불안하지만"\N..이란 표정이야
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna피카소\b0\fs100\bord7\c&H5B24E1&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz11.05\fscx1\fscy1\t(00,100,\fscx50\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscx110\fscy70)\t(200,300,\fscx100\fscy100)\pos(885,785)}뜨끔{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 너희 파트는\NMR로 때워둘 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,핸드싱크 연습만\N착실하게 해올 것!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,안 돼~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,에어밴드가 아니잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,1주일밖에 없는데\N이번은 좀 대충 해도...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,허접해도!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 하면\N열의는 전해질 거라니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-허접...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,아아, 미안...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 둘 다, 처음보다는\N훨씬 잘하게 됐잖아~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,그치, 료~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,흐으음...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,맞장구 좀 쳐줄래!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,아아, 봇치쨩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,토관 속에\N틀어박히지 말자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:03.17,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn@a유치원m\fs75\bord6\c&H2D2D2D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(m 1138 954 l 1136 930 1146 898 1158 868 1174 840 1204 808 1236 794 1254 782 1282 770 1312 766 1340 766 1366 766 1390 774 1380 756 1366 730 1352 702 1346 674 1340 648 1340 614 1348 578 1366 538 1398 496 1430 472 1466 452 1498 444 1540 438 1588 446 1616 458 1920 0 0 0 0 1080)\move(1030,5,600,-1450,00,6010)\frx354\fry6\frz294.8\t(00,6010,\frz288.9\frx358\fry2)}자작사좀했다고또좀깝쳐서죄송합니다.금방깝쳐버리저같은인간은이토관처럼어두침침하고축축해보이는장소가
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아아...!\N봇치타령이 울려서...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,오오...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.21,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿금방 깝쳐버리는\N저 같은 인간은
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.67,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿이 토관처럼 어두침침하고\N축축해 보이는 장소가…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}어라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}나는 둘째 치더라도...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}못 친다구?\N고토 씨가?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}전에 학교에서\N들었을 때는
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}생초보인 내가 들어도\N잘 치는 거 같았는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,아무튼, 얼른~\N나오자~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}저번에 그건...\N우연이었던 걸까?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,리듬섹션만 잘 치면\N어떻게든 될 거야~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,그..럴까요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,응~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,모두가 료급으로\N연주할 수 있게 되는 걸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,요구하는 건\N아니라고 보거든
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그럼\N뭘 보시는 걸까요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,흐음~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,열기?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드로서의 성장?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,성장...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,고마워
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,연습에 어울려줘서
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!\N아..아니에요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 어두운 데가 아니라\N그냥 교실에서 연습하는 게...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)}그것이...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그런 짓을 했다간\N다들!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}「왜 키타 씨 같은 애가\N저런 애랑?」이라면서
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뚫어져라 볼 테니까\N연습할 상황이~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그렇구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.15,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(400,580)\alpha&H60&}어?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.15,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(890,580)}어?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,교실에서 연습하면\N시끄러울 테니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 고토 씨야!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}좋은 쪽으로\N해석해줬어~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}상냥해~{\fna두리둥실}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,있지, 고토 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,나 말야
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,그 후로\N좀 생각해봤는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"밴드로서의 성장"이라면
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,요컨대, 열심히 하는 게\N전해지면 된다고 보거든
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 예...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,난 그때가 오면 진심으로\N"열심히 했다"고 할 수 있게...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,후회하지 않게\N하고 싶거든
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,그러니까\N오디션 날까지
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,부디 어울려주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,에..에이!\N고개 드세요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저야말로\N잘 부탁드립니다아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,머리 모양이\N또 왜 그래...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔 짓거리들이니...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,배..밴드맨으로서의 성장을\N겉모습으로 표현...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,한 거래요...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 료 짓이었나~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}음주
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}흡연
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}여자놀음
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}그리고 머리 모양을\N바가지 헤어로...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}그것이 밴드맨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}이미지가\N너무 치우쳐 있잖아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,980)}그리고 담배든 술이든\N스무살이 된 다음부터!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:12.42,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,10)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\c&H599849&\3c&HFFFFFF&}※ 비틀즈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 바가지 머리♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,응...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,만족했어?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카한테는 눈을 반쪽 가려서\N짜증나는 느낌인
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,비스듬 앞머리\N담당이 비어 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,그딴 담당\N필요 없습니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저기이...
