Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}결국은\N성장이란 게 뭔지...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}전혀 모르겠더라
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만\N지금 나는...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이렇게 넷이서\N찬양받으면서
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}계속 밴드를\N해 나가고 싶어!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩의 진짜 꿈도\N이뤄주고 싶고!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그러니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이런 오디션 따위에서\N떨어질 수는 없어!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이대로...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드를\N끝내버리긴 싫어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}감사합니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}-감사합니다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮지 않나?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,..라고\N하고 싶은 참이다만
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,드럼,\N어깨에 너무 힘 들어갔다
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,기타 두 명,\N왜 바닥만 보고 있냐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,베이스는\N너무 자기 세상에서만 살고
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도, 씁...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 너희가 어떤 밴드인지는\N알 수 있었지만 말야
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,조언...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,감사합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,리액션이\N왜 그러냐...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,그치만...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,그니까 뭔 밴드인지\N알았다고요...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,여기\N기뻐할 부분이거든?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,아마 합격이라고\N말하시는 거 같은데요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,그러니까\N내 말이 그 말이잖냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,합격이라고!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,정말, 언니~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜\N못 알아먹겠다구~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어어어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다시 말해서\N성공했다는 뜻...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}해냈다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,합격이래요!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.76,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿해냈구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.92,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿아아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.06,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿고토 씨!\N해낸 거라구~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:19.34,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿아, 예...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿고토 씨~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.63,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿네!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,료도 눈치챘어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩의 연주...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,아주 잠깐이었지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)\pos(960,980)}평소랑은\N완전 딴판이었던 듯한...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,00)\pos(960,980)}그래도\N고토 씨, 역시 굉장하더라!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,키타 씨,\N죄송한데요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,우읍...!
