Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}-방금 전의 연주...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}-기분 탓이었나...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,죄..죄송해여...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,안 하던 짓을 해서\N위산이 대량으로...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아, 괜찮아~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,그야\N위도 놀랄만 하지~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,설마 하던\N합격이었는데!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,난 처음부터\N확신했었어
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,다음 곡도\N다 생각해뒀고
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,굉장해~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 선배야!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 끝난 다음에\N무슨 소린들 못하겠어~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,다 같이\N사진 찍어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,우..우선 바닥 청소\N하게 해주세요...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}역시...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}상당히 잘 치는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}그래도
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}팀 플레이 경험이 부족한 게\N명백하게 보이네
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}자신감이 부족해서\N제 실력을 발휘 못하고 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}이녀석이라면...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}좀 더\N성장할 수 있을 텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}점장님, 아까부터\N계속 눈 맞는 거 같은데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}자신감을\N키워주려면
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}자기를 인정해주는 인간이\N있단 걸 가르쳐줘야지
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}노려보는데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}화났나!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아까 너무 깝쳐서\N그런 걸까아...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,너는...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,내가 제대로\N보고 있거든?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs100\bord6}끄억…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}완전히 찍혔어...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른, 고토 씨!\N사진 찍자~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}인생 종료...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,점장님~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,솔직히 처음부터\N쟤네들 내보낼 생각이었죠?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,딱 보이는 게~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 스케쥴,\N계속 한 자리 비워놨잖아요
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 그렇게\N심술 부린 거예요?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,심술을 부리긴\N누가...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,납득 못했으면\N내보낼 생각 없었거든...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,아직\N덜 다듬어지긴 했어도
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔가 느껴지는 건\N있었으니까
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,가족인 내가\N엄하게 대하면서
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드를 키워주는 편이\N좋을 거 아녀?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,이런 걸\N시스콘이라고 하던가요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,그 이야기 계속하면\N짜른다?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,예~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 라이브날까지\N더 열심히 해서
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1105,980)\fad(00,600)}밴드 레벨\N올려 나가자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.03,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs70\frz336.2\pos(960,725)}오~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.03,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs70\frz336.2\pos(704,590)}오…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.03,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs55\frz336.2\pos(450,505)}오...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,신곡 가사\N잘 부탁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,점점 더 즐거워지기\N시작했지, 고토 씨!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}마..맞아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}끝나기는 무슨!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}오히려!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}우리, 결속밴드의 모험은\N이제부터 시작이다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 티켓 목표 할당량은\N1,500엔이 20장이니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,한 명당 5장씩!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}할당량이 5장...?
