Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,5장이란 말이죠?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,알겠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}할당량 5짜앙...!
